Keep Nosh in main chat and delegate specialist work via Task to `/bmad-<specialist>`.
Specialist shims run `node .bmad-ml/dispatch-pi.mjs <specialist> <prompt-file>`.

Delegation map:
- LR (literature review) -> bmad-sova
- TA (theory/math) -> bmad-sage
